In the last line, the equivalent 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

dotless
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 infix syntax (
\begin_inset listings
inline true
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

s zip t
\end_layout

\end_inset

) is shown to illustrate a syntax convention of Scala that we will sometimes
