\begin_inset Formula $n_{k}$
\end_inset

 needs to be stopped at 
\begin_inset Formula $k=4$
\end_inset

.
 The sequence of digits then becomes 
\begin_inset Formula $\left[5,0,4,2\right]$
\end_inset

